Description: A multi-panel tabbed file manager with built-in VFS, optional
 udisks-based device manager*, customizable menu system, and bash integration.
 SpaceFM is a fork of legacy PCManFM.  Earlier versions of this program were
 released under the name PCManFM-Mod.  * This package is built with deprecated
 HAL support in place of udisks (device manager functions are limited).

